Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Roosevelt 100th anniversary, 1982
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wtsj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Feb 1982
White House lunch celebrates Roosevelt's centenary - as Reaganomics removes his legacy. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less